  <brief_title>Antibiotic Prophylaxis in Rectal Cancer Surgery: Oral With Intravenous Versus Intravenous Antibiotics.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of Antibiotic Prophylaxis in Rectal Cancer Surgery: Oral With Intravenous Versus Intravenous Antibiotics.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
